Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.46,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}在满是人影的街道尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:20.74,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}有你在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:23.93,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}重复着同样场面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:27.83,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}改变了每天都一样的生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:31.36,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}微笑的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.26,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}明明那么的一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.79,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}在迷茫与过去之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.35,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:43.84,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}赐予了我光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:48.89,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}想永远永远的留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:53.90,OP_CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8}{\fad(200,200)}用力拥抱着那份爱
